SAM 3 — Batch Video Tracking + Evaluation
==========================================

For each folder under --input-dir:
    b1.MP4  +  b1pf.xml (GT)
    ↓
    SAM3 tracking → b1pf_pred.xml  (CVAT track format, matches GT schema)
    ↓
